~ start
if GameState.get_value(GameState.HAS_LEFT_ARM) != true:
	There is one robot arm on the table.
	You try putting your right arm socket near it. Nothing happens.
	You try putting your left arm socket near it. It snaps magnetically into place, with a surprising amount of force.
	do GameState.set_value(GameState.HAS_LEFT_ARM, true)
	do SoundEffects.play_take_arm_sound()
	set parent.visible = false
else
	There is no longer anything on the table here.
=> END
